item.title: 【Requests】[REQ VID] - Elton John and Bernie Taupin: Gershwin Prize for Popular Song
item.description:
"Elton John and Bernie Taupin: Gershwin Prize for Popular Song" tribute show, recorded at the DAC Constitution Hall, in Washington D.C. on March 20th, 2024. The Tribute Show was aired nationwide on PBS on April 8, 2024.

Hi, Does anyone have this show recorded ? I'd Love the full show in 1080 or better. Thanks
